nodes.title: KSampler settings
widgets_values:
You can test and find the best setting by yourself. The following table is for reference.

| Model            | Steps | CFG |
|---------------------|---------------|---------------|
| Offical             | 50               | 4.0               
| fp8_e4m3fn             | 20                | 2.5               |
| fp8_e4m3fn + 4steps LoRA    | 4               | 1.0               |

**VAE**

- [Comfy-Org/qwen_image_vae.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image_ComfyUI/tree/main/split_files/vae)

Model Storage Location

```
📂 ComfyUI/
├── 📂 models/
│   ├── 📂 unet/
│   │   └── put diffusion model here...
│   ├── 📂 loras/
│   │   └── put lora here...
│   ├── 📂 vae/
│   │   └── put vae here...
│   └── 📂 text_encoders/
│       └── put both text encoders (main and mmproj here)...
```
